name: Into The Space (DELVE) (DELVE)
description: Hello Everyone! I am an "Indie Developer" from Delve Interactive Entertainment and here is a very challenging game for everyone. Some levels are designed for hardcore gamers. Choose as per your ability by entering into a new mode called "My Map" in which you choose any map according to your ability.  I hope you enjoy this game, and a new feature is on its way coming very soon, so don't forget for updating your app.
